    "These products 245 are validated for accuracy, provide continuity over time, cover the entire globe, and are freely accessible.",
    "While Google Earth Engine (GEE) provides a platform for processing and analyzing geospatial data, satellite products excel in their focus, accuracy, long-term continuity, global coverage, and accessibility.",
    "However, satellite products do have limitations such as spatial and temporal resolution, cost and infrastructure requirements, data processing challenges, limited spectral bands, coverage gaps, validation difficulties, and integration issues.",
    "These factors can 250 affect their accessibility, accuracy, and usability for certain applications.",
    "Nonetheless, satellite products remain invaluable tools for environmental monitoring, research, and decision-making, providing global coverage and longterm data continuity."
